http://www.greenlink.org:80/affinity/11097/herbal.html 206.86.202.14 19970119094935 text/html 4082
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 10:17:40 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
