http://www.greenlink.org:80/affinity/11097/whales.html 206.86.202.14 19970119095150 text/html 5719
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 10:19:56 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
