http://www.greenlink.org:80/affinity/101196/wolves.html 206.86.202.14 19970119100456 text/html 6318
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 10:33:00 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
