http://www.greenlink.org:80/affinity/120196/sprawl.html 206.86.202.14 19970119095711 text/html 4257
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 10:25:13 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
