http://www.greenlink.org:80/affinity/11097/clearcut.html 206.86.202.14 19970119094830 text/html 4996
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 10:16:33 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 4825
Last-modified: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 15:45:10 GMT
