<h3 align=left><a href="#Return to Top of Page" name="Articales">Articles:</a></h3>
<table width=100%>
<tr><td width=50%><a href="#DIOXINS AND EAGLES">Dioxins and Eagles	</a>: </td><td width=50%><a href="#&quot;GRAVY TRAIN&quot;">&quot;Gravy Train&quot;</a> : </td></tr>
<tr><td width=50%><a href="#TAKE THE MONEY:">Take the Money</a> : </td><td width=50%><a href="#STEWARDSHIP UNDER SIEGE SAYS DEFENDERS">Stewardship Under Siege Says Defenders</a> : </td></tr>
