<H2>Doing Business With Us</H2>
<p>At UT Automotive, we pride ourselves in offering the highest quality products to the Automotive OEM's. We are continually seeking long term partnerships with our supply base to develop the world class quality necessary to survive in today's environment.
<p><CENTER><STRONG>UT Automotive can offer over &#36;500 million of new business per year!</STRONG></CENTER>
<p>To become eligible as a supplier to UT Automotive, you must meet our certifications requirements including superior quality, delivery and technology at world class cost levels. To prepare you for doing business with UT Automotive, below are some of the policies and procedures required of our supply base:
<ul><li>QS9000</li>
<li><A HREF="/doing/ethics.htm"><B>Code of ethics</B></A></li>
<li>Standard purchasing agreement</li></ul>
<p>To help both of us succeed, a <b><A HREF="pie.htm">Partners in Excellence</A> </b>manual has been written as a guideline to quantify how UT Automotive manages its supply base. Additionally, a Product Development Launch Process has been formalized to insure successful product introduction to our customers.
<p>To be considered as a potential supplier for current and future business, please submit the Supplier Profile.
<p>In the near future, as opportunities arise, this site will allow approved suppliers to view and quote UT Automotive business opportunities online.

