http://www.uta.com:80/protech/prod.htm 165.207.2.80 19970208060539 text/html 2360
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 06:09:45 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 06-Nov-96 15:32:38 GMT
Content-length: 2166
