<DOCHDR>
http://www.uta.com:80/doing/ethics.htm 165.207.2.80 19970208060710 text/html 11563
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 06:11:10 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 26-Sep-96 22:59:40 GMT
Content-length: 11369
Content-type: text/html
