<h2>Wire Harnesses</h2>

UT Automotive is an industry leader in the production of automotive wire harnesses. We design and build
everything from one-piece harnesses to multiplex systems, and our extensive testing and prototype
facilities ensure the highest quality products.
<P>
UT Automotive has automated its production processes and created synchronous manufacturing cells in many
of its operations to increase flexibility, reduce costs and accommodate just-in-time
manufacturing. 
<p>
We are leaders in automated production of modular harness subassemblies. Individual circuits are
cut, stripped, terminated and plugged into a hard-shell connector to form the subassembly.
Advanced sensing devices ensure components are built to exact specifications and standards.
<p>
Our ability to produce custom-built vehicle wire harnesses in accordance with individual feature
content of a vehicle eliminates unused circuits and improves just-in-time delivery.
<p>
And UT Automotive's warranty analysis program ensures continuous improvement of our products, and has
resulted in lower warranty expense for our customers and "best-in-class" warranty performance for
many car lines.

