<h2>Door and Side Wall Trim</h2>

<IMG SRC="images/door.gif" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH="384" HEIGHT="175">
<p>
UT Automotive can design and manufacture front, rear and quarter interior door trim panels using a variety
of processes and materials to match a customer's styling and cost requirements.

<P>
For example, UT Automotive can provide a complete door panel - bolster, carpet, map pocket, etc. - as
one molded piece, thus eliminating many pieces and assembly steps and significantly improving
finish and texture match.
<P>
UT Automotive also conducts an ongoing test and development program in side impact energy absorption in
order to design and manufacture interior door trim panels with improved driver and passenger
safety performance.

