<h2>Headliners and Sun Visor Systems</h2>

<p>
UT Automotive provides a complete range of standard and modular headliners and is the largest
independent producer of headliners for the automotive industry.
<P>
With our experience in materials research and manufacturing processes, UT Automotive can deliver
headliners that provide optimal structural and acoustic performance. And an intensive research
program is working to develop new, environmentally safe substrates for use in headliners and other
products.
<P>
UT Automotive also designs and manufactures a full range of sun visors to meet our customers' cost and
styling requirements. Visors can integrate many components, including lamps, mirrors and
sunshade extensions.
<P>
UT Automotive is working to move vanity lights from the sunshade to the headliner for more natural
lighting and to lower costs. And our new concealed sunshade slides into the headliner, offering
improved adjustability and more headroom.

