<H2>Input Controls</H2>


<CENTER><IMG SRC="/images/ic_imag1.jpg"></CENTER><BR>

UT Automotive is an industry leader in the production of automotive Input Controls. We design and build
everything from multifunction turn signals to mecha-tronic devices, and our extensive testing and prototype
facilities ensure the highest quality products.
<P>
<TABLE BORDER=0>
     <TR>
          <TD>UT Automotive has automated its production processes and created synchronous manufacturing cells in many
of its operations to increase flexibility, reduce costs and accommodate just-in-time
manufacturing. </TD>
<TD>  </TD>
          <TD>And UT Automotive's warranty analysis program ensures continuous improvement of our products, and has
resulted in lower warranty expense for our customers and "best-in-class" warranty performance for
many car lines.</TD>
     </TR>
</TABLE>


