<HEAD>
<TITLE>UT Automotive Products: Rear Vision Systems</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#173973" VLINK="#777777" ALINK="#C8D838" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<map name="products">
<area shape="rect" coords="361,23, 449,53" href="/jobs/jobs.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="268,23, 362,54" href="/doing/doin.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="201,00, 268,67" href="/protech/prod.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="114,23, 201,54" href="/media/medi.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="34,23, 115,53" href="/general/gene.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="00,22, 34,54" href="/index.htm">
</map>

<IMG SRC="../PROD.GIF" ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="68" BORDER="0" usemap="#products" border="0">
</center>
<!--header ends here-->
<h2>Rear Vision Systems</h2>

<p>
UT Automotive designs and manufactures a full range of exterior rear-view mirror systems to meet customer
cost and styling requirements. UT Automotive uses state-of-the-art paint systems and motor systems, and
special attention is paid to vibration and wind noise.
<P>
UT Automotive provides the following mirror types:
<ul>
<li>Foldaway.
<li>Heated.
<li>Manual remote.
<li>Electric remote.
<li>Electric memory.
<li>Electrochromatic.
<li>Power foldaway.
</Ul>
<p>
Finishing capabilities include base coat/clear coat painting and unpainted (black) UV stable
material.
<P>
UT Automotive's engineering and manufacturing facilities are close to customers, which ensures better
communication and just-in-time delivery. A UT Automotive team works with a customer from concept
through launch at designated assembly plants so changes and concerns can be addressed quickly.
<P>
UT Automotive can design and manufacture a complete rear-view system. We have a team of research and
development engineers working specifically on rear-vision system enhancements such as directional
indicators, display characteristics and ultrasonic cleaning.

