<IMG SRC="../PROD.GIF" ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="68" BORDER="0" usemap="#products" border="0">
</center>
<!--header ends here-->
<h2>Insulation/Acoustical Products</h2>

<p>
Headliners, package trays, sail panels and B and C pillar covers are only a
few of the many acoustical decorative trim products produced by UT Automotive. We also
manufacture a variety of insulation products for various vehicle applications.
<P>
Our wide range of products and exceptional design and engineering capabilities
enable us to offer acoustical support from the body shop to the trim shop.
<P>
UT Automotive conducts extensive testing of materials in its own labs, at the
<a href="http://www.utrc.utc.com/">United Technologies Research Center</a>
and at leading universities. We have created, and continually update, a data
base of all insulation materials based on absorption rates and sound
transmission loss rates to help determine the best insulation and absorption
materials to meet customer requirements.
<P>
Our research and testing program also has enabled us to identify more
environmentally friendly materials.

