<head>
<title>UT Automotive Products: Engineered Elastomers</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#173973" VLINK="#777777" ALINK="#C8D838" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<map name="products">
<area shape="rect" coords="361,23, 449,53" href="/jobs/jobs.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="268,23, 362,54" href="/doing/doin.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="201,00, 268,67" href="../prod.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="114,23, 201,54" href="/media/medi.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="34,23, 115,53" href="/general/gene.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="00,22, 34,54" href="/index.htm">
</map>

<IMG SRC="../PROD.GIF" ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="68" BORDER="0" usemap="#products" border="0">
</center>
<!--header ends here-->

<h2>Engineered Elastomer Products</h2>

<P>
UT Automotive manufactures sealants, adhesives and acoustical rubber products. Our
EPDM and nitrile vinyl rubber technologies enable us to extrude special shape
profiles or continuous length sheets, which are used to eliminate wind, road
and engine noise as well as buzzes, squeaks and rattles.
<P>
Our body shop and paint shop sealants and adhesives satisfy a wide range of
customer needs, including gaskets and tapes.
<P>
Our Presst-O-Plug features a high-expansion sealant extruded around a
compressible rubber core.  It provides a consistent, lightweight pillar seal
that significantly reduces noise traveling through the pillars into the
passenger department.
<P>
UT Automotive also combines its rubber and sound-deadening sealant technologies for an
innovative acoustical seal between the windshield and instrument panel. These
additional capabilities enable us to offer customers a total vehicle
acoustical package.

