<h2>Electronic Modules</h2>

<IMG SRC="images/mod1.gif" ALIGN=textTOP WIDTH="240" HEIGHT="194"><IMG SRC="images/mod2.gif" ALIGN=textTOP WIDTH="246" HEIGHT="194">
<p>
UT Automotive designs and manufactures a wide range of electronic control modules, which
provide a reliable link with other components and systems.
<P>
Functions include drive-away protection modules, illuminated entry, power
window control, multipurpose timing control, and electronic heating,
ventilation and air conditioning controls.
<P>
UT Automotive also can provide complete vehicle multiplexing architecture, multiplex
electronic nodes and smart nodes integrated into the vehicle junction box.



