<H2>BREED Technologies to Acquire UT Automotive Steering Wheels Operations
</H2>
<STRONG>DEARBORN, Mich., Sept. 23, 1996</STRONG>  UT Automotive and <A HREF="http://www.breedtech.com">BREED Technologies</A>  announced an agreement by which BREED will acquire the steering wheels operations of UT Automotive.  The proposed acquisition is expected to be completed as soon as possible following any required regulatory reviews.  Terms of the agreement were not disclosed.
<!--footer begins here-->
<p>
<CENTER>
