  <head>
    <title>
      UTA Reduces Workforce at Newton, Ill, Plant
    </title>
  </head>

  <body bgcolor="#ffffff">

    <p align="center">
    <img src="/images/heads/about.head.gif" width="550" height="150"
    alt="[about uta]">
    </p>

    <h5>
      Contact: Michael Scholl
