    <h2>2. Global facilities</h2>



    <P>
    UTA has 89 manufacturing plants in 17 countries - the United States, Canada,
    Mexico, England, Ireland, France, Germany, Hungary, Italy, Spain, Portugal,
    Honduras, the Philippines, Argentina, Thailand, China and South Korea.
    <P>
    The company has engineering centers in Dearborn, Detroit and Troy, Mich.;
    Koln, Germany; and Asti, Italy. And other technical centers and sales
    offices are in Garde (Paris), France; Munich, Germany; Goteberg, Sweden;
    Valls, Spain; Tokyo and Nagoya, Japan; and Cebu, Philippines.

<p>    <p align="center">
      <a href="/general/info/closer.htm">[back]</a>
