<HEAD>
<TITLE>UT Automotive Manufacturing Capabilities</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#173973" VLINK="#777777" ALINK="#C8D838" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<map name="general">
<area shape="rect" coords="362,23, 449,54" href="/jobs/jobs.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="273,24, 363,54" href="/doing/doin.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="198,23, 274,53" href="/protech/prod.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="122,24, 199,53" href="/media/medi.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="47,00, 122,67" href="../gene.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="01,23, 34,54" href="/index.htm">
</map>
<IMG SRC="../gene.gif" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="73" usemap="#general" border="0">
</center>
<!--header ends here-->
    <h2>6. Manufacturing and Materials Process Capabilities</h2>



    <p>
    UT Automotive is leading the way with design, engineering and process capabilities to
    accommodate the ever-changing global automotive market.
    <P>
    UT Automotive works with a wide selection of skin, substrate and energy and noise
    absorbing materials; and with the latest in process technologies and
    equipment, including rim, slush, double slush, rotocast, extrusion,
    injection, compounding and compression capabilities.
    <P>
    Combining these abilities allows UT Automotive to provide a full spectrum of options
    to meet our customers' styling objectives in cost and finish. We can create
    the desired color, texture and feel for virtually any trim component.
    <P>
    UT Automotive has the ability to utilize different materials and processes - for
    example, endothermic, counter-pressure and gas-assist moldings. We minimize
    sink and work, thus minimizing defects and waste. And programmable
    equipment, end-of-arm tooling and robots provide quick mold change.
    <P>
    More importantly, our ability to manufacture a diverse group of interior
    systems and components ensures continuation of design and flow within a
    vehicle's interior, which results in superior fit, optimized assembly and
    cost savings.
    <P>
    These capabilities have enabled UT Automotive to be named program manager for the
    entire interior of a number of vehicles.  



    <p align="center">
      <a href="/general/info/test.htm">[back]</a>
      <a href="/general/info/process.htm">[top]</a>
      <a href="/general/info/quality.htm">[next]</a>
