<HEAD>
<TITLE>UT Automotive World-Class Quality</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#173973" VLINK="#777777" ALINK="#C8D838" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<map name="general">
<area shape="rect" coords="362,23, 449,54" href="/jobs/jobs.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="273,24, 363,54" href="/doing/doin.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="198,23, 274,53" href="/protech/prod.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="122,24, 199,53" href="/media/medi.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="47,00, 122,67" href="../gene.htm">
<area shape="rect" coords="01,23, 34,54" href="/index.htm">
</map>
<IMG SRC="../gene.gif" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="73" usemap="#general" border="0">
</center>
<!--header ends here-->
    <h2>7. World-Class Quality</h2>



    <p>
    UT Automotive recognizes that a companywide commitment to quality is required to be a
    world-class supplier.
    <P>
    Our quality support system utilizes statistical process control, design of
    experiments, failure mode effects analysis and other continuous quality
    improvement techniques.
    <P>
    At our European facilities, we offer real-time data collection of
    significant characteristics, which is shared on line directly with our
    customers.
    <P>
    UT Automotive continues to find new ways to deliver world-class quality to our
    customers. Examples include:
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Concurrent design and engineering</strong>, which builds in
      quality earlier in the process and reduces design-to-product cycle time.
      <li><strong>Cell manufacturing</strong>, which combines people and
      equipment in smaller manufacturing groups (cells) to reduce set-up time,
      accommodate smaller lot sizes and provides just-in-time flexibility.
      <li><strong>Bar coding</strong>, which facilitates communication between
      departments and suppliers and, in turn, improves productivity and
      delivery.
      <li><strong>Partners in Excellence</strong>, which enables UT Automotive to
      recognize our best suppliers and helps us more effectively control
      quality, time and costs. UT Automotive also participates with its suppliers in a
      joint materials development program.
      <li><strong>Regularly scheduled preventive maintenance</strong>, which
      minimizes downtime, increases production and improves just-in-time
      capabilities.
      <li><strong>On-site representation in customer plants</strong>, which
      ensures better coordination and flexibility.
      <li><strong>Continuous training</strong>, which ensures better
      decision-making skills.
      <li><strong>Participatory management</strong>, which enables employees at
      all levels and stages to find opportunities for continuous quality
      improvement.
      <li><strong>Continuous improvement</strong>, which uses Kaizen principles
      and our own production systems such as UT AutomotivePS and flexible manufacturing to
      produce higher quality and productivity.
    </Ul>
    <p>
    UT Automotive's goal is to deliver the highest quality product possible. But ensuring
    product quality does not stop when it is delivered to the customer. UT Automotive is a
    leader in tracking reliability of products in the field. Warranty data is
    analyzed and corrective action in design and/or assembly is taken to provide
    a trouble-free product. The result has been lower warranty expenses for our
    customers.

    <Hr>

    <p align="center">
      <a href="/general/info/process.htm">[back]</a>
      <a href="/general/info/quality.htm">[top]</a>
      <a href="/general/info/pm.htm">[next]</a>
    </p>

