<!--header ends here-->

    <h2>8. Program management</h2>


    <p>
    Many suppliers can manufacture products. But UT Automotive also excels in managing the
    process, which is critical to the success of a program.
    <P>
    UT Automotive manages the entire process to ensure timeliness, cost control and
    quality. By forming cross-functional management teams, UT Automotive is able to
    streamline the process and improve communications, and the result is better
    design and tooling, improved timing, continuous improvement and controlled
    costs.
    <P>
    UT Automotive teams work directly with OEM designers, engineers and platform teams,
    and customer plants, and coordinates efforts with other suppliers. 


    <p align="center">
      <a href="/general/info/quality.htm">[back]</a>
      <a href="/general/info/pm.htm">[top]</a>
      <a href="/general/info/sysint.htm">[next]</a>
    </p>

