<!--header ends here-->

    <h2>11. Training/Human Resources</h2>


    <p>
    Achieving world-class levels of excellence requires new ideas, new methods
    and improved skills. That's why UT Automotive invests thousands of hours and dollars
    each year in training - from associates on the shop floor through the
    highest managerial ranks.
    <P>
    Solid training programs allow UT Automotive to maintain a highly skilled staff that
    can effectively serve our customers now and in the future.
    <P>
    UT Automotive also is constantly adding to its staff, hiring experienced design and
    engineering people who can enhance our capabilities.
    <P>
    In addition, our leadership development program identifies future leaders
    of UT Automotive, ensuring a continuous chain of high-caliber, team-oriented managers.
    <P>
    UT Automotive's training and human resources programs lead to better communication and
    understanding among our people and facilities, nurtures a spirit of teamwork
    and strengthens our ability to provide world-class quality and delivery.



    <p align="center">
      <a href="/general/info/rnd.htm">[back]</a>
      <a href="/general/info/hr.htm">[top]</a>
    </p>

