<area shape="rect" coords="01,23, 34,54" href="/index.htm">
</map>
<IMG SRC="../gene.gif" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="73" usemap="#general" border="0">
</center>
<!--header ends here-->
    <h2>Dick Sloan</h2>
    <h3>President, UT Automotive Europe</h3>
    <IMG SRC="pics/sloan.gif">

    <hr>

    <P>

    <STRONG>Richard J. Sloan</STRONG> was named president of UT Automotive's European operations on July 13,
    1994. He had served as interim president of UT Automotive Europe since 
    September 1993.
    <P>
    Sloan, 56, joined UT Automotive in 1981 as vice president, finance and chief
    financial officer of UT Automotive Europe.
    <P>
    In 1985 he was named vice president and controller of UT Automotive's 
    Automotive Productions division and became the division's vice
    president of operations in 1986.
    <P>
    He was named vice president and chief financial officer of UT Automotive's 
    Interior Systems in 1989. And in 1991 he became president of the
    Hose Fittings and Industrial Products division.
    <P>
    Before joining UT Automotive, Sloan was employed at Chrysler Corp. for 17 years.
    <P>
    Sloan holds both a bachelor's degree in finance and economics and a master's
    of business administration (MBA) degree from the University of Detroit.
    <P>

