    <h2>Michael O. Brown</h2>
    <h3>Vice President, General Counsel</h3>
<IMG WIDTH=182 HEIGHT=260 BORDER=0 SRC="/general/people/pics/brown.gif">
<p>

    <strong>
Mike Brown </strong>was named vice president, General Counsel on Sept. 1, 1996. He is responsible for the company's legal function and its services.<p>

Brown joined UT Automotive in 1995 as general counsel. He has been with <A HREF="http://www.utc.com">United Technologies Corp.</A> (UTC) since 1981 and has held a series of key positions with <A HREF="http://www.utc.com/pweh.htm">Pratt & Whitney</A>, <A HREF="http://www.sikorsky.com">Sikorsky</A> and at UTC's corporate office.<p>

Brown has a bachelor's degree from Eisenhower College and master's and law degrees from <A HREF="http://www.syr.edu">Syracuse University</A>. 
