<h2>Employment Opportunities</h2>
UT Automotive is an internationally recognized supplier to the automotive industry. Strengths such as systems integration
capabilities and a broad product line make UT Automotive a preferred supplier of automakers worldwide.

<p>

The success of UT Automotive in the global marketplace is dependent upon the excellence of the employees it attracts. Our Fortune 100, Tier 1 company provides an exceptional compensation program and benefits package. UT Automotive is an equal opportunity employer seeking qualified candidates in the following areas:

<P></P>

<ul>
<li>Engineering/Technical</li>
<li>Finance/Accounting</li>
<li>Human Resources</li>
<li>Information Technology</li>
<li>International</li>
<ul><li><A HREF="jobs3072.htm">General Manager - China Joint Venture</A></li></ul>

<li>Operations</li>
<li>Purchasing/Material Control</li>
<li>Quality</li>
</ul>
<p>



If you're interested in a position at UT Automotive, send a copy of your resume:

<ul><li>via fax to: (313) 593-3825</li>

<li>via e-mail (in ASCII format) to: <a href="mailto:staffing@uta.com">staffing@uta.com</A></li>

<li>via mail to: UT Automotive, Human Resources, 5200 Auto Club Drive, Dearborn, MI 48126-9982

</ul><p>

