<!-- Source File: prodserv.html -->


<CENTER><!-- Graphic Tag -->
<IMG WIDTH=586 HEIGHT=78 BORDER=0 ALT="Products and Services"ALIGN=TOP SRC="prodmast.gif"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>

<FONT SIZE=4>Aspen is very interested in helping you learn about the products and services that we offer. We want to assist you with thoughtful, cost-effective business applications that can help with your information management needs. We hope that you find the information within our Web site informative and thorough. To help you quickly locate the service or product that would be most applicable to your needs, we have listed brief descriptions of what you will find by linking to other pages within this site or to products that we have created.<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<A HREF = "services.html">Services</A>. Provides information on the wide range of information management services that Aspen has been providing to clients for 30 years. We offer services in information dissemination; litigation support; survey and evaluation; telecommunications; systems design, development, and administration; communications; and many other areas.<P>

<A HREF = "aspenweb.html">Aspen-Developed Web Sites</A>. Includes links to the many commercial and government Web sites that Aspen developed.<P>

<A HREF = "http://www.housinglink.com">HousingLink<IMG SRC="sm.gif" Border=0></A>. Links you directly to the home page of HousingLink<IMG SRC="sm.gif" Border=0>, a Web site published by Aspen that provides extensive housing and community development information.<P>

<A HREF = "http://www.aspensys.com/hisfocus/">Health Information Services  (HIS) Newsletter</A>. Connects you to HIS FOCUS, the electronic version of our quarterly newsletter for healthcare professionals that is a source for details on information systems management, patient account and coding news, pharmacy topics, and collection tips as well as updates on Aspen's latest products and services for healthcare information management.<P>

<!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="http://www.aspensys.com/emain.html">Energy Monitor Newsletter</A>. The online version of our newsletter for various energy services
organizations and energy consumers. Energy Monitor contains articles on innovative market
research, new products, and services being offered in the energy sector. Readers are also kept
abreast of Aspen's range of products and services offered to this vital sector of the economy.



</BLOCKQUOTE>
</FONT>

