<H2><CENTER>*<A HREF="ico.html">Internet Career Opportunities</A>*</CENTER></H2>
Aspen offers its employees competitive salaries and an attractive benefits
package. Among the benefits is participation in the Employee Stock Ownership
Plan (ESOP), which enables Aspen's professionals to assume responsibility
for their own success.</P></CENTER>

<P> Listed below are positions currently open at Aspen. For further information,
contact Kevin Attanasio at (301) 251-5443, e-mail <B><A HREF="MAILTO:kattanasio@aspensys.com">kattanasio@aspensys.com,</A></B>
or Hank Miller at (301) 251-5075, e-mail <B><A HREF="MAILTO:hmiller@aspensys.com">hmiller@aspensys.com.</A></B>
Please fax your resume with the appropriate reply code to (301) 251-5445.</P>

<P> <!-- List Tag --></P>

