<H2>Internet Services</H2>

<H3>Graphic Artists/Web Designers<BR>
Rockville, Maryland</H3>

<P><B>Job Responsibilities:</B> Support Web site development and maintenance
activities.</P>

<P> <B>Skill Requirements:</B> Demonstrable knowledge of HTML, Photoshop,
and inline plug-ins such as QuickTime required; familiarity with Shockwave
and JAVA a major plus. Knowledge of traditional desktop packages for the
MAC, including Freehand, Illustrator, Pagemaker, and Quark desired. Portfolio
review required. Please include URL addresses of WWW sites that you have
designed in your response.</P>

<P> Freelance and full-time positions available.</P>

<P> <B>Reply to Code:</B> HM-WGAWD</P>

<P> <!-- Horizontal Line Tag -->
<HR></P>

<H3>PC/Internet Help Desk<BR>
Rockville, Maryland</H3>

<P><B>Job Responsibilities:</B> Perform installations and upgrades of PCs,
software, Web browsers and other client software, problem solving, help
desk support for Internet-related questions, and user training.</P>

<P> <B>Skill Requirements:</B> Experience providing help desk support in
a PC/Netware environment. Solid knowledge of desktop software, DOS, Windows,
office automation, printers, modems, and use of Web browsers such as Netscape
and Mosaic.</P>

<P> <B>Educational Requirements:</B> Bachelor's degree in Computer Science,
Electrical Engineering, Information Systems Management, or related field
required.</P>

<P> <B>Reply to Code:</B> KA-WPC/Int</P>

