such as CGI (especially Perl), database links, Java applets, multimedia
services, and electronic commerce. Administration of listservs, gophers,
WAIS databases, FTP sites, and Web servers.</P>

<P> <B>Skill Requirements:</B> Knowledge of HTML 2.0, 3.0, and Netscape
extensions; Unix shell and CGI scripting (Perl); Online databases; Windows
NT, Java, and related tools.</P>

<P> <B>Educational Requirements:</B> Bachelor's degree in Computer Science,
Electrical Engineering, Information Systems Management, or related field
required.</P>

