<HTML> 

<HEAD><TITLE>Services</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#127CBB" VLINK="#CA0904"> 


<CENTER><!-- Graphic Tag -->
<IMG WIDTH=586 HEIGHT=78 BORDER=0 ALT="Services"ALIGN=TOP SRC="isdsvmst.gif"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

<CENTER><table border=0 width=460 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
<tr>
<td>


<P><FONT SIZE=5 color=brown><B>Aspen Internet Services</B> . . .</FONT><BR>

<I>offering comprehensive innovative business applications</I></P>


<P>The Internet is changing the way organizations communicate, market goods and services, and conduct business in fundamental and dramatic ways.  The speed and efficiency of the Internet have created business opportunities unlike ever before. To take advantage of these opportunities, many organizations are creating an Internet presence. Aspen Internet Services can help you achieve results through innovative Internet business applications and technology.</P>
<BR>



<P><FONT SIZE=4 color=brown><B>Are You Tangled Up in the 'Net?</B></FONT></P>





<P>Aspen can unravel the mysteries of today's Internet technologies and identify how these technologies can  benefit your organization. As expert consultants and developers, we have created some of the most innovative business applications and information management tools for our clients. To get a better idea of Aspen's comprehensive Internet offerings, take a closer look at what we can provide your business:</P>



<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="gdsfs.html">General Development Services</A>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="marketfs.html">Marketing Assistance</A>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="transfs.html">Electronic Commerce and Secure Transactions</A>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="hostfs.html">Web Site Hosting</A>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="intrafs.html">Intranet Development </A>
</UL>



<P>Through the use of Internet technologies, Aspen can help you:</P>

<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>communicate with customers, vendors, and distributors
<LI>enhance customer support
<LI>streamline ordering through electronic commerce
<LI>improve internal communications and operations through an intranet
<LI>market goods and services
<LI>reach new markets
</UL>
 


<P>So, whether you're planning an Internet presence, looking to improve an existing site, or ready to take the next step toward more innovative Internet applications, we have the solution for you. By analyzing your current operations and markets, we can provide tailor-made, results-oriented Internet applications for all your business needs.</P>

<BR>


<I><FONT SIZE=3 color=brown>Creating innovative Internet applications for your business</FONT></I>



<P>To create a successful Internet presence, you need an experienced team of specialists who understand the balance of technology, design, and content. Aspen gives you that, and more. We provide a full menu of services to meet the simplest to the most complex 
requirements, and we keep you aware of new Internet technologies. Plus we service all your Internet needs with no outsourcing, so you benefit from a coordinated, responsive, cost-effective approach.</P>

<P>We offer:</P>

<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>consulting services to help identify how your business can benefit from an Internet presence or intranet
<LI>secure transactions capabilities
<LI>design and development of interactive features
<LI>Internet marketing and promotions support
<LI>assistance with content development and maintenance
<LI>high-impact graphics and multimedia
<LI>customized business applications
<LI>systems support and integration
</UL>
<BR>

<P><FONT SIZE=4 color=brown><B>Aspen Internet Services -- Providing Full-Service Systems Support</B></FONT></P>



<P>Aspen can supply you with hosting services, network development, database design, and ongoing maintenance. We help evaluate your technology resources and advise 
you on the best Internet options. We adjust our service levels as your needs or in-house capabilities change. Our services include:</P>

<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>helping you gain access to the Internet
<LI>determining systems requirements
<LI>installing, configuring, and integrating hardware and software
<LI>building firewall security measures
</UL>
<BR>

<FONT SIZE=3 color=brown><I>Ensuring your success with customer support</I></FONT>



<P>Aspen's support doesn't stop once your Internet services are up and running, because we know that ongoing maintenance is critical for success. We provide training, user documentation, and usage and activity reports. We also go a step farther to provide end-user support for your customers through telephone hotlines and supporting documentation.</P>





<P>With Aspen as your partner, you are assured of technically advanced yet user- friendly Internet applications and services. For three decades we have been a leader in applying technology to information management needs. For more information on how Aspen Internet Services can assist you, please contact us at <!-- MailTo Tag -->
<A HREF="MAILTO:info@aspensys.com">info@aspensys.com</A> or</P>





<P><BLOCKQUOTE><B>Aspen Internet Services</B><BR>
Aspen Systems Corporation<BR>
1600 Research Boulevard , Rockville, MD  20850<BR>
Toll Free: (888) 851-7472<br>
Fax: (301) 251-5111<BR>
E-mail: <!-- MailTo Tag -->
<A HREF="MAILTO:info@aspensys.com">info@aspensys.com</A><BR>
<!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="http://www.aspensys.com">www.aspensys.com</A></BLOCKQUOTE></P>
<BR>
<BR>


<CENTER><!-- Graphic Tag -->
