<HEAD><TITLE>Partnerships</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#127CBB" VLINK="#CA0904"> 


<!-- Graphic Tag -->
<IMG WIDTH=586 HEIGHT=78 BORDER=0 ALT="Partnerships"ALIGN=TOP SRC="isdprtmt.gif">
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><table border=0 width=460 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
<tr>
<td>

<FONT SIZE=3>

<P>Aspen Internet Services is dedicated to helping you establish or optimize your Web-related 
resources.  We provide turn-key Internet and intranet development services at an affordable 
cost.  To better serve our clients, Aspen has entered into strategic partnerships to help you 
and your company make the most of your business.</P>

<BR>
<BR>





<P><!-- Graphic Tag -->
<!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="http://www.bbnplanet.com"><IMG WIDTH=332 HEIGHT=64 BORDER=0 ALT="BBN Logo" SRC="bbnplanet.gif"></P></A>



<BLOCKQUOTE><P>Aspen Internet Services recently established a channel 
partnership with BBN Planet, one of the largest Internet 
solution service providers in the United States.  Through 
this partnership, Aspen will be able to offer our clients a 
wide variety of Internet access and security management 
services.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>
