of software and services for managing information.  One 
of Oracle's strengths is in providing scaleable enterprise 
solutions, along with an ongoing commitment to 
promoting and supporting open standards.  Aspen's 
clients will benefit from the power and flexibility of 
Oracle's client/server applications, development tools, and 
database products.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>
