<HTML> 

<HEAD><TITLE>Sample Designs</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#127CBB" VLINK="#CA0904"> 

<!-- Graphic Tag -->
<IMG WIDTH=586 HEIGHT=78 BORDER=0 ALT="Sample Designs"ALIGN=TOP SRC="isdsdmst.gif">
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><table border=0 width=460 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
<tr>
<td>
<FONT SIZE=3>

<P>The Web offers many creative opportunities for an organization to develop an exciting, colorful, and lively online image. There are many design approaches that can be implemented to help an organization achieve a desired look. To help you begin thinking about a design that may be best suited for your individual needs, Aspen has created several home pages based on some commonly used approaches appearing on the Web today. We hope you find the sample designs interesting. Please keep in mind that we can work with you to create a design presentation that meets your exact requirements, whether it entails a high-tech interface or a simple, conservative approach.</P>

<BR>

<FONT SIZE=4><B><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="biomed.html">Clean and Contemporary</A></B></FONT>



<P>This design offers a clean, modern look. It offers a fresh, uncomplicated presentation for site visitors, and uses contemporary style graphics and design elements that portray a simple, sophisticated look. This particular treatment enables an organization to create a progressive image using a simple presentation.</P>
<BR> 

<P><FONT SIZE=4><B><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="spinner.html">Column Style</A></B></FONT></P>

<P>The column design style conveys a dynamic, active image with a presentation similar to a newsletter. The design offers the ability to simultaneously convey large amounts of information on a home page, and it quickly and easily highlights new announcements.  This design is ideal for dynamic, text-intensive sites with requirements for frequent updating.  </P>
<BR>

<P><FONT SIZE=4><B><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="radio.html">Contemporary With Animation</A></B></FONT></P>

<P>This design approach offers added creativity to a home page by incorporating animated graphics. The subtle use of the animation provides excitement, without overusing the technology. This form of presentation would be appealing to organizations that want to use various design features available from the Web, without detracting from the message needing to be conveyed.</P>
<BR>

<P><FONT SIZE=4><B><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="spachome.html">Aggressive With Sophisticated Animation</A></B></FONT></P>


<P>Our most aggressive design sample uses very sophisticated features to capture the attention of the Web user.  It incorporates high-level graphics, clever use of text, and high-end animation.  This design would be perfect for companies seeking to convey a "cutting edge"  image.</P>

</FONT>

</td>
</tr>
</table></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>

