<HEAD><TITLE>Price Information</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#127CBB" VLINK="#CA0904"> 
<!-- Graphic Tag -->
<IMG WIDTH=586 HEIGHT=78 BORDER=0 ALT="Price Information"ALIGN=TOP SRC="isdprmst.gif">
<BR>
<BR>

<CENTER><table border=0 width=460 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
<tr>
<td>
<P>

<FONT SIZE=4 color =brown><B><I>Effective September 1, 1996. Prices subject to change.</I></B></FONT>

<P>



<P>Aspen Systems Corporation can provide attractive prices for Web site development and other Internet services. Due to the variety of requirements that individual clients may have, Aspen develops a separate project budget for each client that reflects their particular needs. Our services range from designing and developing World Wide Web sites to installing, configuring, and integrating hardware and software. Listed below are Aspen's standard fees.</P>


<BR>

<P><FONT SIZE=4 color=brown><B>Web page production:  $100 - $410/page</B></FONT></P>



<P>Web page production costs cover document and image conversions; HTML coding; formatting; layout of text, graphics, and navigational icons; proofreading; and hypertext quality assurance. Price per page varies based on the size, amount of text, number of graphics/images, special design considerations, and use of specialized features.</P>


<BR>



<P><FONT SIZE=4 color=brown><B>Graphic design of masthead and navigational icons:  $800</B></FONT></P>



<P>Graphic design services include creation of overall design scheme for Web site, including home page, secondary pages, and navigational icons.</P>


<BR>

<!-- Graphic Tag -->


<P><IMG WIDTH=460 HEIGHT=8 BORDER=0  SRC="isdhplne.gif"></P>



<FONT SIZE=4 COLOR=BROWN><B>Professional Services Rates </B></font><br>

