<TD WIDTH=20%><FONT SIZE=3><B>$65/hr</B></FONT><BR></TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=2><I>Creation of customized applications/features</I><P></TD></TR>

<TR><TD><FONT SIZE=3><B>Sr. Internet Programmer</B></FONT></TD>
<TD WIDTH=20%><FONT SIZE=3><B>$100/hr</B></FONT><BR></TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=2><I>Senior-level technical support, network requirements, server setup</I></FONT><P></TD></TR></Table>
<BR>

<!-- Graphic Tag -->
<IMG WIDTH=460 HEIGHT=8 BORDER=0  SRC="isdhplne.gif">
<BR>

<A NAME="hostfees"></A>


<P><FONT SIZE=4 color=brown><B>Web Site Hosting Fees</B></FONT></P>

Features of Aspen's pricing structure include:
<UL><LI> a one-time fee for basic server set-up<P>
<LI> an optional service for registering a Web site domain name with InterNIC<P>
<LI> a basic monthly hosting fee that is based on disk space and number of hits<P>
<LI> add-on fees for storage and traffic once a predetermined level is reached<P>
<LI> low fees for additional hosting services, such as databases, forms, discussion forums, and secured access<P>
</UL>
Rates for each level of service, as well as additional services, follow. We will assist clients in determining which service level is most appropriate and cost-effective, based upon current Web site requirements.<P>

<UL><LI> <B>Level One Service -- </B>ideal for small-to-medium sites that have a minimum amount of  storage and bandwidth requirements.<p>
<B>Basic monthly rate: $50.00</B><BR>(includes 5 MB of storage and up to 10,000 hits/month)<P>

<LI> <B>Level Two Service -- </B>for medium-to-large sites that have a moderate amount of storage and bandwidth requirements.<p><B>Basic monthly rate: $100.00</B> <BR>(includes 15 MB of storage and up to 25,000 hits/month)<P>

<LI> <B>Level Three Service -- </B>for medium-to-large sites that have greater-than-average storage and bandwidth requirements.<p>
<B>Basic monthly rate: $150.00</B><BR>(includes 50 MB of storage and up to 50,000 hits/month)<P>

</UL>
<DL><DT> <B>Basic Set-up (one-time fee):</B> $200.00 (all levels)<P>
<DT> <B>Additional storage:</B> $5.00/5 MB/month (all levels)<P>
<DT> <B>Additional usage:</B> $10.00/1,000 hits/month (all levels)<P>
<DT> <B>Optional InterNIC registration:</B> $150.00 (all levels)<BR>
(includes the initial 2-year registration fee of $100.00)<P>
</DL>

<br>
