<HEAD><TITLE>General Development Services</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#127CBB" VLINK="#CA0904"> 


<!-- Graphic Tag -->
<CENTER><IMG WIDTH=540 HEIGHT=72 BORDER=0 ALT="General Development Services"ALIGN=TOP SRC="gdsmst.gif"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><table border=0 width=460 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
<tr>
<td>


<FONT SIZE=3><P>Aspen's team of experienced Internet professionals can provide technical, design, and publishing support for your Internet or Intranet.  We use state of the art Internet technologies and business applications, ensuring that you receive the most technically sound, user-friendly, and cost-effective Web site or intranet.  Our services include: </P>



<P><B><I>Consulting Support Services</I></B>.  Aspen can assist in all phases of Web site development, including site planning, site design, content development, implementation of specialized features, and use of emerging technologies. </P>


<P><B><I>Design and Graphics Services</I></B>.  Aspen's design staff have expertise in the technical areas of Web site design, coding, and structure.  Our Web designers use state-of-the-art features including animation, frames, multimedia, and image maps.</P>


<P><B><I>Production Support</I></B>.  Our production services include HTML coding, file conversions, scanning, and digitizing of audio and video clips.</P>

<P><B><I>Editorial Services</I></B>.  Aspen's editors have extensive experience in organizing materials and content for Web sites so that users are able to quickly locate desired information.  Our Web editors are skilled in the nuances that are unique to electronic publishing, including how to identify appropriate hypertext links and navigational icons/buttons.  In addition, we offer Web proofreading support, which requires a different skill set than that required for traditional print publishing.</P>


<P><B><I>Programming and Network Support</I></B>.  Our technical staff can provide systems development support that would include implementation of secure transaction and electronic commerce features; database design and programming; development of specialized Web features requiring programming through CGI scripting or Java; evaluation of Internet services such as FTP, Gopher, Newsgroup, or Web servers; network design and integration; Internet access; staff training; and performing requirements analysis. </P>


<P><B><I>Training</I></B>.  Aspen provides training support to its customers in areas such as basic Internet use and understanding, HTML, use of Web editing tools, and Web site maintenance.  These training services are customized to meet our clients' specific staff or Web site maintenance needs.</P>


<P>If you would like a cost estimate for developing an Intranet or a Web site, call (888) 851-7472 or e-mail us at <!-- MailTo Tag -->
<A HREF="MAILTO:info@aspensys.com">info@aspensys.com</A>.</P></FONT>


</td>
