<HEAD><TITLE>Marketing Assistance</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#127CBB" VLINK="#CA0904"> 



<CENTER>
<!-- Graphic Tag -->
<IMG WIDTH=540 HEIGHT=72 BORDER=0 ALT="Marketing Assistance"ALIGN=TOP SRC="marktfs.gif"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><table border=0 width=460 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
<tr>
<td>
<FONT SIZE=3>

<P>Aspen offers a full range of marketing assistance, including consulting, the development and implementation of marketing plans, and the development of marketing and sales materials. Three levels of marketing support for Web sites are available.  We also customize marketing programs based on client need.</P>
<BR>



<P><B>Level 1 -- Basic online marketing support</B></P>

<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>registration of site with top 20 general search engines and directories (for example, Yahoo, Alta Vista, Excite)
<LI>registration of site with 10 more narrowly defined search engines/directories (for example, health/medicine directories)
<LI>announcement of the site on Aspen's home page, with a link to the site
</UL>

<P>Includes registration of site using key words/categories and confirmation of the site's listing.
</P>
<BR>



<P><B>Level 2 -- Online marketing and general publicity</B></P>




<P>Includes all Level 1 services, plus the following:</P>


<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>writing and issuing a press release about the site to up to 30 general and trade publications
<LI>writing an announcement bulletin or flier for customers (81/2 x 11, 2-sided, 2-color)
<LI>writing an announcement bulletin or flier for employees/internal distribution
<LI>consulting on how to integrate the site's URL on existing marketing communications vehicles, i.e., letterhead, business cards, brochures, advertising, packing or billing statements, etc.
</UL>
<BR>



<P><B>Level 3 -- Comprehensive marketing communications plan</B></P>




<P>Includes all Level 1 and 2 services, plus the following:</P>



<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>development of a marketing communications plan to introduce and promote the site.  Elements include:
</UL>



<!-- List Tag -->
<UL TYPE=square>
<BLOCKQUOTE><LI>planning and writing a direct mail campaign for targeted audiences (list purchase not included)

<LI>designing and writing an advertisement announcing the site (media placement not included)

<LI>consultation on cost-benefits of exhibits or possible tie-ins with special events

<LI>consultation on cost-benefits of Internet advertising; design and production of the ad</BLOCKQUOTE>
</UL>

