<HTML> 

<HEAD><TITLE>Intranet Development</TITLE></HEAD> 

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#127CBB" VLINK="#CA0904"> 


<!-- Graphic Tag -->
<CENTER>
<IMG WIDTH=540 HEIGHT=72 BORDER=0 ALT="Intran Development"ALIGN=TOP SRC="intramst.gif"></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER><table border=0 width=460 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
<tr>
<td>


<FONT SIZE=3><P>Today, companies are seeking to develop intranets at a faster rate than they are establishing an Internet presence. The result of this trend will be a revolution in the way organizations do business.</P>



<P>In the past, private information management networks were often beyond the resources of most organizations.  However, through today's rapidly evolving technologies and the development of intranets, companies are now able to afford the benefits of a comprehensive information management system.  By using common Internet technologies, in conjunction with their own business applications, organizations can communicate, distribute information, and facilitate project collaboration and management across their entire enterprise, including remote locations. The results include:</P>

<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>increased employee productivity 
<LI>reduced costs
<LI>less paperwork
<LI>higher profit margins
</UL>

<P>Additionally, organizations are finding intranet development both easy and inexpensive.  Intranets are user-friendly, platform independent, and universally accessible, and most important, the technology is readily available.</P>


<P>Among the information resources and management tools organizations are placing on their intranets are:</P>

<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI>collaborative groupware applications
<LI>legacy databases and systems
<LI>computer-based training
<LI>electronic and database publishing
<LI>e-mail
<LI>management resources
</UL>



<P>Aspen can help your organization develop an intranet by providing support in the following areas:</P>


<P><B><I>Consulting</I></B>. Aspen can assist in all phases of intranet development, including site planning and design, content development, and implementation of interactive features and new technologies.</P>

<P><B><I>Production</I></B>. Aspen can provide page production support, including HTML coding, data conversion, scanning, document imaging, proofreading, and editorial support.  </P>



<P><B><I>Programming and Networking</I></B>. Aspen's technical staff can provide systems development support including database design and programming, development of specialized intranet features requiring CGI scripting or Java/Javascript, network design and integration, and requirements analysis.</P>


<P><B><I>Staff Training</I></B>. Aspen can provide your staff with training in intranet server set-up and HTML and other programming languages used to develop and maintain your intranet.</P>


<P><B><I>Internal Promotion</I></B>. Aspen can provide consulting services to assist with promoting the use of the intranet among your organization's employees.</P></FONT>

</td>
</tr>
</table>
<BR>
<BR>

