<HEAD><TITLE>ERIC - Details About this Site</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY bgcolor="white" link="blue" vlink="teal" background="bgtile.gif"> 

<!--HEADER-->

<TABLE width=550 border=0 cellpadding=5>

<TR valign=top>
	<TD rowspan=100><A HREF = "navbar.map"><img border=0 src="navbar.gif" alt="Navigation Bar" ISMAP></A></TD>
	<TD rowspan=1 colspan=3><IMG SRC="details.gif" alt="Details About this Site"></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
	<TD colspan=3><HR size=5></TD>
<TR>

<TR>
<TD colspan=3>
<A HREF="barak.html"><H2>Links to all
 ERIC Sites</H2></A>
 Provides links to more than 30 ERIC-sponsored Web and Gopher sites
 that deal with education.<p>
 <A HREF="whatsnew.html"><H2>What's New</H2></A>
 Tells what's new on the ERIC Systemwide Web Site and in the ERIC
 system.
 
 <A HREF="site.html"><H2>ERIC Site of the Week</H2></A>
 Reveals the hidden treasures in ERIC's section of cyberspace. 
 
 <A HREF="http://www.cua.edu/www/eric_ae/search.html"><H2>Search the
 ERIC Database</H2></A>Lists and links to known, publicly available Web, Gopher,
 Telnet, and TN3270 sites for searching the ERIC database. If you
 have questions about the ERIC database, please refer to <A
 HREF="about2.html">About the ERIC
 Database</A>.
 
 <A HREF="pubs.html"><H2>ERIC
 Systemwide Resources</H2></A>
 Numerous products to help you access and use the information in the
 ERIC system.
 <p>
 <A HREF="faq.html"><H2>FAQs About
 ERIC</H2></A>Tells everything you ever wanted to know about ERIC,
 and then some.
 
</TD>
</TR>

