<html>

<Head><title> Happy Birthday ERIC</title>

</head>

<BODY bgcolor="white" link="blue" vlink="teal" background="bgtile.gif"> 
<TABLE width=550 border=0 cellpadding=5>

<TR valign=top>
	<TD rowspan=100><A HREF = "navbar.map"><img border=0 src="navbar.gif" ISMAP></A></TD>
	<TD rowspan=1 colspan=3><FONT color="000080" SIZE=5><B>ERIC Plans Year-Long 30th Anniversary Celebration</B></FONT></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
	<TD colspan=3><HR size=5></TD>
</TR>


<TR>
	<TD colspan=3>

The Educational Resources Information Center, a nationwide education information network sponsored by the <A HREF = "http://www.ed.gov/">U.S. Department of Education</A>, <A HREF = "http://www.ed.gov/NLE/">National Library of Education</A>, turns 30 years old in Fall 1996. As part of the year-long anniversary commemoration during the 1996-97 school year, plans are under way to:

<ul><p>

<li>Produce a special anniversary issue of the ERIC Review featuring system highlights, photoreproducible training materials, and thoughtful discussion of the uses of education information.

<p>

<li>    Administer a treasure hunt (with prizes) on the World Wide Web.

<p>

<li>   Distribute premiums, including posters, bookmarks, folders, and other goodies.

<p>

<li>Premier full-text delivery of ERIC documents via the Internet in Spring  1997.</ul>

<p><p>


<quote>"We want to make sure we celebrate ERIC's 30-year mark with a substantive gift to the education community," said Blane Dessy, Director of the National Library of Education, ERIC's organizational home within the Department of Education. "That's why we're focusing resources on developing materials that will help people understand and use ERIC more effectively. Full-text, in particular, will help our customers and ensure that ERIC continues to harness technological advances to support education at all levels." </quote>

<Hr size=5><BR
clear=left> </TD</TR> <TR>
<TD colspan=3> <CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=-1>
	<A HREF = "barak.html">Links to all ERIC Sites</A> | 
	<A HREF = "whatsnew.html">What's New</A> | 
	<A HREF = "site.html">Site of the Week</A> | 
	<A HREF = "http://www.cua.edu/www/eric_ae/search.html">Search the ERIC Database</A><BR>
	<A HREF = "pubs.html">ERIC Systemwide Resources</A> | 
	<A HREF = "faq.html">FAQs About ERIC</A> | 
	<A HREF = "details.html">Details About This Site</A> | 
	<A HREF = "index.html#erictop">Home</a>
<P>last update 11/01/96</P>
<P>ACCESS ERIC, <a href=mailto:acceric@inet.ed.gov><I>acceric@inet.ed.gov</I></P>
