<title> Definition: CIJE</title>

<strong><i>Current Index to Journals in Education </i></strong> also commonly refered to as <strong>CIJE</strong>

is a paperbound monthly (12 issues per year) index journal that announces journal articles from over 700 education and 

education-related jourals.  Each issue announces appproximately 1,500 items and is available on subscription from <a href="http://www.oryxpress.com">ORXY Press</a>.
</DOC>
