including enrichment programs, talent searches,
summer programs, accelerated university programs,
and other special programs.
URL: <a href="http://www.eskimo.com/~user/kids.html">http://www.eskimo.com/~user/kids.html </a>
<p>
<i>The ERIC Systemwide Web Site.</i> Offers links to
useful resources for gifted children. 
URL: <a href="http://www.aspensys.com/eric/">http://www.aspensys.com/eric/</a>
<p><B>
Listservs 
</b><P>
<I>GiftedNet-l.</I> Send e-mail to
<a href="mailto:listserver@listserv.cc.wm.edu">listserver@listserv.cc.wm.edu</a>. In the text line
type "Subscribe giftednet-l (firstname lastname)."

<P><I>TAG-L.</i> Send e-mail to <a href="mailto:listserv@vm1.nodak.edu">listserv@vm1.nodak.edu</a>. In
the text line type "Subscribe TAG-L (firstname
lastname)."

<p><I> TAGFAM</i>. Send e-mail to
<a href="mailto:listserv@sjuvm.stjohns.edu">listserv@sjuvm.stjohns.edu</a>. In the text line type
"Subscribe TAGFAM (firstname lastname)."
<center><p><hr><FONT COLOR="333333"><b>
