Classroom."  <i>Young Children</i>, 44 (1), 10-15.  EJ 380 635.
<p>
For more information on this subject, contact:<address><pre>

	ERIC Clearinghouse on Reading and Communication Skills
	Indiana University, Smith Research Center
	2805 East 10th Street, Suite 150
	Bloomington, IN 47408-2698
	(812) 855-5847
	(800) 759-4723
	 <a href="http://www.indiana.edu/~eric_rec/">http://www.indiana.edu/~eric_rec/</a>
</pre></address><HR>
