Lawler, S., & Vance, M. (1988).  "Kindergarten:  New Directions With An
Old Philosophy."  <I>Reading Improvement</I>, 25 (3), 233-36.  EJ 383 783.
<p>
Phillips, D. (1987).  <I>Quality in Child Care:  What Does Research Tell
Us?</I>I  Washington, DC:  National Association for the Education of Young
Children.<P>
For more information about preschool programs, contact:<ADDRESS><PRE>
      ERIC Clearinghouse on Elementary and Early Childhood
      Education
