      (800) 583-4135
      <a href=http://ericps.ed.uiuc.edu/ericeece.html">http://ericps.ed.uiuc.edu/ericeece.html</a>

      National Association for the Education of Young Children
      1834 Connecticut Avenue NW
      Washington, DC 20009-5786
      (202) 232-8777

      National Association of State Boards of Education
      1012 Cameron Street
      Alexandria, VA  22314
      (703) 684-4000
</ADDRESS></PRE><hr>
