<title> Definition:EDRS Price</title>

The <strong>ERIC Document Reproduction Service (EDRS) availablility</strong> field that tells you how much the document will cost if you 

wanted to order it from the ERIC Document Reproduction Service. In the Example 

given <strong>EDRS Price-MF01/PC15 Plus Postagage</strong> "MF" means microfiche; 

"PC" means reproduced paper copy. When described as "Document Not Available from EDRS",

sources are cited in the record. See the latest <a href="price.html">price code schedules</a> for pricing information.
</DOC>
<DOC>
