</DOCHDR>
<title> Definition: ISSN</title>

<dt><b>ISSN-International Standard Serial Number</b>

<dd>a <strong>Interternational Standard Serial Number</strong> more comonely refered to as the <strong>ISSN Number</strong> is a

unique identifying number assigned by publishers to each distict

serial publication.  Documentshave a simmilar number assigned to them called the <a href="defisbn.html">ISBN</a>
</DOC>
