<title> Definition: RIEDEC93</title>

<dt><b>CIJEDEC93</b>

<dd>This notation </strong>CIJEDEC93</strong> means that this record first

appeard in the print index <a href="defcije.html"><i>Current Index to Journal in Education</i></a> in December 1993.
</DOC>
