<title> Definition: Identifiers</title>

<strong>Identifiers</strong> are terms that are assigned to the document or article that characterize

proper names or concepts not yet represented by <a href="defdes.html">descriptors</a>.

Identifiers come from the <a href="defial.html"><i>Identifier Authority List</i></a>.  Major identifiers are preseded 

by an asterisk.
</DOC>
