<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#00000" LINK="#3B17FF" VLINK="#FF0900">

<CENTER><H2>Energy Services</H2></CENTER><BR>

 <FONT SIZE=4>
 Aspen offers specialized energy services to electric and gas utilities, commercial/industrial, and
 government clients. Aspen's Energy Services focus on data collection and analysis which ensure
 optimal customer service and sound market data to make informed energy utilization decisions.
 In the deregulating and competitive energy field, timely and accurate data, insightful analysis,
 and enhanced customer service will be the keys to success. Aspen's Energy Services focus on
 these needs. The following areas encompass Aspen's expertise in these areas:<P>


 
 <H3>Customer Research and Analysis</H3><P>


 
<!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="resear.html">Customer/Market and Load Research</A><BR>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="stat.html">Statistical Analysis and Modeling</A><BR>

<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="eval.html">Utility Program Evaluation</A><BR>

<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="outsour.html">Load Research Outsourcing</A><BR>

<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="tech.html">Technical Support Services</A>
</UL> <P>


 <H3>Customer Services</H3><P>


 
 <!-- List Tag -->
<UL>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="audit.html">Energy Audit Programs</A>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="dist.html">Distribution and Fulfillment Services</A>
<LI> <!-- Link Tag -->
<A HREF="dsm.html">Utility DSM Services</A>
</UL><P>


 
 <H3>Software</H3><P>


 
 <!-- List Tag -->
<dir>
<LI><!-- Link Tag -->
