<IMG align=left hspace=10 SRC="aspnbug3.gif">
<H2>Aspen Introduces "Competitive Edge Services"<BR>
 
to Strengthen Utilities' Competitive Position</H2><P>


<FONT SIZE=4>Aspen introduces a line of "Competitive Edge Services" that will enable electric utilities to enter the competitive electricity market with either an aggressive or defensive strategy.  These services are designed to strengthen utilities' positive relationships with their existing customers and provide services that will attract prospective customers.<P>


	Aspen's Competitive Edge Services presently include:

<UL>
<LI>A low-hassle turnkey financing program that promotes strong customer relationships;
<LI>A software package for tracking customer marketing information;
<LI>A marketing research project that identifies the threats and opportunities in onsite generation;
<LI>A marketing research project that identifies the opportunities for promoting electrotechnologies;
<LI>A marketing research project that identifies peak-reduction potential available through customer service programs;
<LI>A marketing research project that identifies technical services that will produce a contractual relationship with your customers.
</UL>  <B>For further information, call Dr. Harley Barnes at 1-800-638-2784.</B></FONT><P>


