<TITLE>HIS Focus, Fall 1994</title><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<H3><IMG align=bottom SRC="hismast.gif"><BR>An Information Newsletter for 
Health Care Professionals, Fall 1994</H3>
<A NAME="inthis"><IMG SRC="inthis.gif"></A><H2><MENU>
<LI><A HREF="hospbene.html">Hospitals Benefit From Aspen's Management of Their 
Medical Record Departments</A>
<LI><A HREF="oigrept.html">OIG Releases Report on Coding Physician Services</A>
<li><A HREF="scalesec.html">Rx FOR SUCCESS: Scale Your Systems Security Level 
To Value and Content</A>
<li><A HREF="jcaho.html">1994 JCAHO Information Management Standards 
Announced</A>
<li><A HREF="vcodes.html">Coding Corner: Focus on V-Codes</A>
<li><A HREF="hcfapubs.html">HCFA Publishes 1995 Coding and DRG Changes</A>
