een pre-approved by the Contracting Officer's Representative (COR). There is an estimated 4- to 6-week turnaround to start a task.<P><I>For more information, call Jim Lloyd at (703) 578-1850 or e-mail <A HREF="MAILTO:jlloyd@aspensys.com">jlloyd@aspensys.com</A>.</I></P><BR><CENTER><IMG border=0 SRC="redbar.gif"></CENTER><BR>

