<H2><A name="oak">Aspen's Oak Ridge
Office Gets a New Area Code</A></H2><P>


    <FONT SIZE=4>Aspen's Oak Ridge, Tennessee office has a new area code 423.  Our phone number therefore becomes (423) 482-2721 and our fax number is (423) 482-7314.</FONT><P>


<HR>

<H2><A name="customer">Bob St. Amand to Lead Aspen's Customer Service Programs</A></H2><P>


     <FONT SIZE=4>Aspen is pleased to announce that Robert St. Amand has 
recently joined our firm as Group Manager for Customer Service Programs.  
In this capacity, Bob will have overall responsibility for Aspen's 
utility customer service program operations, including energy audit 
programs, shared savings and financing
programs, and customer marketing information systems.  Bob 
joins Aspen from ANCO Engineers, where he served as Director of 
Program Design and Implementation, spearheading the startup 
and implementation of Consumers Power's commercial and 
industrial programs.  Bob's recent activities have focused on developing 
turnkey opportunities in the shared savings area.
<P>     Bob can be reached at 1-800-638-2784.</FONT>

 <HR>
<P>


<H2><A name="page">Aspen Can Set Up Your Company's Internet Home Page</H2></A><P>

  

<FONT SIZE=4>Many utilities, including Baltimore Gas & Electric, 
Electricite de France, Hawaiian Electric, and Green Mountain Power, 
have discovered the many benefits of having an Internet presence.  A World 
Wide Web site on the Internet is an easy and cost-effective way to tell 
customers about products and services, provide general information on the 
company, and offer important and timely consumer information.
<P>     If you don't already have a Web site, now is the time to 
consider one.  Aspen offers a complete range of Internet services, which means you 
can take advantage of our expertise in the energy field as well as our 
Internet experience to create a visually appealing, user-friendly, and 
content-rich site.  We offer consulting and 
needs analysis, World Wide Web site development, systems support 
and integration, Internet marketing and promotions support, and 
customer support.
<P>     Aspen's Web site was recently named a 4-star site by Magellan, one 
of the key Internet directories.  We received Magellan's highest 
possible rating for our overall site design, content, and navigability.   
Several other sites developed by Aspen have received similar industry recognition. 
 Our site can be accessed at <A HREF="http://www.aspensys.com">http://www.aspensys.com</A>.  For 
more information on our Internet services, including a brochure, contact 
Scott Crocket at (301) 251-5126 or via
e-mail at <!-- MailTo Tag -->
<A HREF="MAILTO:scrocket@aspensys.com">scrocket@aspensys.com.</A></FONT><P>


