</CENTER>

<FONT SIZE=4>
Aspen has trained staff competent in the development and support of information systems. These specialists serve as both staff extension to the inhouse resources of Aspen's clients as well as a complete unit for major undertakings that involve all phases of a system's life cycle, from analysis and design to programming and testing.<P>

We specialize in projects that combine information systems development disciplines with other technological areas such as statistical sampling and analysis, survey design and processing, data quality assurance and security, and database publishing and distribution.<P>

