<BR><CENTER><!-- Header Tag -->
<H2>Survey and Evaluation Services</H2><BR>
</CENTER>

<FONT SIZE=4>
Aspen offers the services of a multidisciplinary team of professionals who have demonstrated their customized research in a range of specialized fields, including energy, health, education, and the environment.<P>

Our specialists provide our clients with such services as primary data collection, data analysis, and program evaluation. Moreover, these professionals have extensive experience in study design, database design and management, and quality control and assurance systems. These highly skilled staff are proficient in turning raw data into usable information.<P>

We conduct mail and telephone surveys, personal interviews, and focus groups. Findings from these forms of research help us assist clients with determining appropriate, cost-effective sampling methods and identifying target groups that will yield quality information. Our professionals always work very closely with our clients to ensure that the appropriate results are achieved on time and within budget.<P>

<HR>
For more information, contact Lilly Gardner at <a href=mailto:lgardner@aspensys.com>lgardner@aspensys.com</a><P>

