<HEAD>
<TITLE>IAEA Home Page</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#FF0000">
<CENTER>
<HR WIDTH=90%>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=3 WIDTH=560>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=center ALIGN=center COLSPAN=2>
<font size=+3><B>WELCOME TO THE IAEA</B></font></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=top>
<BR>
The International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) is often called the <A HREF="/uniaea.html">"Atoms for Peace" organization</A> of the United Nations system. 
It carries out activities related to the peaceful development and verification of nuclear 
energy's uses. The <A HREF="/worldatom/glance/profile/statute.html">
IAEA Statute </A>was approved on 26 October 1956 and the Agency came into existence on 29 
July 1957. Our official address is: <I>P.O. Box 100, Wagramerstrasse 5, A-1400 Vienna, 
Austria. Telephone: (+43 1) 2060-0; Fax: (+43 1) 20607; E-mail: Official.Mail@iaea.org</I>.</TD>
<TD ROWSPAN=2 VALIGN=center ALIGN=center>
<IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/iaealogo.gif" alt=IAEA Logo>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
